\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 INT. LUXURIOUS GREAT ROOM\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 DAY}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 John and Jane sit on a silk-tasseled sofa, sipping martinis.}
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\qc\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b1 JOHN}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Oh my goodness, darling, how long have we known and loved each other now? Why, it\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s over twenty years, isn\u8217\'92t it?}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b1 JANE}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Yes, ever since we were at the university together, and your\~}{\f0\fs24\b0 f}{\f0\fs24\b0 raternity threw a mixer and invited the Women\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s Socialist Club. Your house was so rich, we poor girls called Beta Tau Zeta Billions, Trillions, and Zillions.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b1 JOHN}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i1 (gazing around their magnificent home)}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Yes, and then I lost my inheritance. But we both worked very hard over the years to make our dreams come true. And they did, didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t they, my little Trotskyite?}}